                "id": "which-platform",
                "title": "Which Platform Should You Choose?",
                "content": "<p>Choosing the right platform depends on your business goals:</p><ul><li>If your app requires high performance and complex functionalities, choose native development.</li><li>If you need a fast, cost-effective solution with cross-platform support, choose hybrid development.</li><li>For startups and MVPs, hybrid is a great option, while for long-term scaling, native is often the better approach.</li></ul>"
